title: VIOO Makes Bullish Cross Above Critical Moving Average - Nasdaq.com
text: In trading on Thursday, shares of the Vanguard S&P Small-Cap 600 ETF (Symbol: VIOO) crossed above their 200 day moving average of $139.48, changing hands as high as $141.25 per share. Vanguard S&P Small-Cap 600 shares are currently trading up about 2.7% on the day. The chart below shows the one year performance of VIOO shares, versus its 200 day moving average:     Looking at the chart above, VIOO's low point in its 52 week range is $118.07 per share, with $164.21 as the 52 week high point - that compares with a last trade of $141.42.
